<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 20:08:26 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>美国在沙特阿拉伯的利益正受到以色列极右翼救世主部长的破坏</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</link><description>一项有利于以色列安全理论和美国战略的沙特-美国防务协议与内塔尼亚胡在政治上所信奉的弥赛亚观点相冲突，使得以色列成为伊朗的合作伙伴，共同阻挠该协议</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 19:44:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/american-interests-in-saudi-arabia-are-being-torpedoed-by-israels-far-right-ministers/00000190-064e-d067-adb0-8e6e1a840000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨退出内塔尼亚胡政府后，以色列民族团结党民意调查下滑</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-unity-party-down-in-polls-after-gantz-quits-netanyahu-government/00000190-0675-d067-adb0-8e7712f30000</link><description>根据第 11、12 和 13 频道的调查，如果今天举行选举，本尼·甘茨领导的民族团结党将拥有 22-25 个席位，成为以色列最大政党。议会主要集团之间的平衡保持不变</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 19:09:25 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israels-national-unity-party-down-in-polls-after-gantz-quits-netanyahu-government/00000190-0675-d067-adb0-8e7712f30000</guid></item><item><title>在投票反对正统派草案豁免后，利库德集团议员呼吁解雇国防部长加兰特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/after-vote-against-haredi-draft-exemption-likud-lawmakers-call-to-fire-gallant/00000190-083b-d067-adb0-8e3fd2350000</link><description>该党消息人士称，活动人士对国防部长感到愤怒，他是唯一投票反对该法案的联盟成员。利库德集团党魁尼西姆·瓦图里和奥舍尔·什卡利姆呼吁内塔尼亚胡解雇他</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 17:45:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/after-vote-against-haredi-draft-exemption-likud-lawmakers-call-to-fire-gallant/00000190-083b-d067-adb0-8e3fd2350000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战事第 249 天：美国高级官员称哈马斯战后无法统治加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-249-hamas-cannot-rule-gaza-after-war-top-u-s-official-says/00000190-0829-d667-abf0-6ceb14f90000</link><description>哈马斯表示接受美国起草的联合国安理会决议，要求停火并释放所有人质，并准备就其细节进行谈判 ■ 美国国家安全顾问杰克·沙利文表示，哈马斯在战后无法在加沙继续掌权 ■ 发射了 50 枚火箭弹来自黎巴嫩的戈兰高地 ■ 以色列北部城市海法自 1 月以来首次响起火箭警报 ■ 战争进入 249 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:43:20 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-249-hamas-cannot-rule-gaza-after-war-top-u-s-official-says/00000190-0829-d667-abf0-6ceb14f90000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡谈论了一场对抗伊朗核武器的精彩比赛——仅此而已</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</link><description>以色列总理从未制定过一致的政策来对抗伊朗核计划，包括2018年他让特朗普退出核协议时。内塔尼亚胡在国会的演讲中，预计会有更多诸如“西方正面临毁灭”之类的咆哮</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 16:41:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-talks-a-good-game-against-iranian-nukes-and-thats-it/00000190-06ff-d5ad-ad93-26ff98a10000</guid></item><item><title>皮尤调查显示，随着加沙战争的拖延，拜登在以色列人中的支持率下降</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</link><description>对美国总统的信心从 68% 下降至 57%，仅领先特朗普 3 个百分点</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 15:00:17 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/bidens-popularity-among-israelis-drops-as-gaza-war-drags-on-pew-survey-shows/00000190-075f-d0f9-a1d5-d77f6cd90000</guid></item><item><title>包括哈马斯成员在内的四名巴勒斯坦人在约旦河西岸被以色列国防军杀害</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinians-including-hamas-member-killed-by-idf-troops-in-west-bank/00000190-0746-da02-a1dc-ff4f61240000</link><description>在拉马拉附近的一个村庄被杀的巴勒斯坦人中包括一名哈马斯军事部门的成员，他曾在以色列监狱服刑 20 年</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 14:46:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-palestinians-including-hamas-member-killed-by-idf-troops-in-west-bank/00000190-0746-da02-a1dc-ff4f61240000</guid></item><item><title>加沙战争使以色列立法者在征兵法案上存在分歧；利库德集团成员呼吁解雇加兰特</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-divides-israeli-lawmakers-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption-bill/00000190-06d2-dbe3-a1da-17f78b240000</link><description>利库德集团的一位消息人士告诉《国土报》，该党成员对投票反对该法案的国防部长约夫·加兰特感到愤怒，一些人开始要求将他开除出党。</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 12:13:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/gaza-war-divides-israeli-lawmakers-on-ultra-orthodox-army-exemption-bill/00000190-06d2-dbe3-a1da-17f78b240000</guid></item><item><title>内塔尼亚胡和他的政府不值得在战争中死去的士兵的生命</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-government-arent-worthy-of-the-lives-of-soldiers-dying-in-their-war/00000190-06cc-d067-adb0-8eee10b30000</link><description>投票赞成该法案的 63 名议员已经知道加沙拉法的爆炸造成四名士兵死亡。内塔尼亚胡在讨论中狡猾的微笑象征着他的遗产：人民和他们选出的代表之间的脱节</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 11:42:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/netanyahu-and-his-government-arent-worthy-of-the-lives-of-soldiers-dying-in-their-war/00000190-06cc-d067-adb0-8eee10b30000</guid></item><item><title>四名以色列士兵在加沙南部拉法的诱杀房屋爆炸中丧生</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-explosion-of-booby-trapped-house-in-rafah-southern-gaza/00000190-0693-d667-abf0-66dbfe810000</link><description>拉法东部 Shabura 社区一座雷击建筑物爆炸时，Tal Pshebilski Shaulov、Eitan Karlsbrun、Almog Shalom 和 Yair Levin 丧生</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 09:58:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/four-israeli-soldiers-killed-in-explosion-of-booby-trapped-house-in-rafah-southern-gaza/00000190-0693-d667-abf0-66dbfe810000</guid></item><item><title>据《华尔街日报》报道，辛瓦尔告诉哈马斯官员，被杀的加沙平民是“必要的牺牲”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/wsj-sinwar-tells-hamas-officials-that-gaza-civilians-killed-are-necessary-sacrifices/00000190-0627-d067-adb0-8e2793220000</link><description>在《华尔街日报》披露的书面信件中，哈马斯领导人叶海亚·辛瓦尔告诉卡塔尔的哈马斯官员，10 月 7 日“事情失去了控制”，加沙平民的死亡将“为这个国家的血管注入活力”</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 08:20:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/wsj-sinwar-tells-hamas-officials-that-gaza-civilians-killed-are-necessary-sacrifices/00000190-0627-d067-adb0-8e2793220000</guid></item><item><title>甘茨迟来的离开内塔尼亚胡政府的影响可能太小，也太晚了</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-belated-departure-from-the-netanyahu-government-may-be-too-little-too-late/00000190-0323-d5ad-ad93-276b1cae0000</link><description>民族团结党退出联盟未能引发全国范围内的抗议活动，但政府的行为可能会让以色列人重新走上街头 ■ 甘茨和艾森科特的决定表明人们相信内塔尼亚胡仍然受到充分的控制，主要是受到美国反对派的控制 ■ 以色列，由于内塔尼亚胡的明确选择，错过了沙特关系正常化的列车</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 03:00:05 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/gantzs-belated-departure-from-the-netanyahu-government-may-be-too-little-too-late/00000190-0323-d5ad-ad93-276b1cae0000</guid></item><item><title>哈马斯向路透社提交了对以色列人质释放和停火提议的回应</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-live/biden-on-un-cease-fire-resolution-hamas-must-prove-it-wants-a-deal/00000190-0517-d5ad-ad93-255fa9c30000</link><description>布林肯会见八名美国人质以色列人质的家人 ■ 美国驻联合国大使：以色列已准备好推进停火人质协议 ■ 美国国务院：美国将为加沙和约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦人增加 4.04 亿美元的援助 ■ 以色列的报道黎巴嫩：以色列国防军袭击黎巴嫩南部的卡法克拉和纳古拉村 ■ 以色列军队在约旦河西岸逮捕行动中杀死四名巴勒斯坦人 ■ 《华尔街日报》援引辛瓦尔写给哈马斯官员的信：加沙平民被杀是“必要的牺牲”</description><pubDate>Tue, 11 Jun 2024 02:32:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-live/biden-on-un-cease-fire-resolution-hamas-must-prove-it-wants-a-deal/00000190-0517-d5ad-ad93-255fa9c30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列不反对美国和哈马斯就美国人质达成单独协议</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-not-opposed-to-separate-deal-between-u-s-and-hamas-for-american-hostages/00000190-0404-dd57-abb4-7e4ef7880000</link><description>布林肯在耶路撒冷开会警告内塔尼亚胡：拜登政府人质协议的失败可能导致整个框架崩溃</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:34:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article/.premium/israel-not-opposed-to-separate-deal-between-u-s-and-hamas-for-american-hostages/00000190-0404-dd57-abb4-7e4ef7880000</guid></item><item><title>前总理的妻子利希·拉皮德 (Lihi Lapid) 发现以色列作家在美国面临的严峻新现实</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lihi-lapid-wife-of-ex-pm-discovers-grim-new-reality-for-israeli-authors-in-america/0000018f-fea3-d5ad-ad8f-feeb80280000</link><description>莉希·拉皮德本应该在美国进行新书巡演，庆祝她的小说《On Her Own》的英文版发行。相反，她正在特拉维夫参加抗议活动，发现现在没有人愿意接待一位以色列作家，甚至连反对派领导人的另一半也不想接待</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 21:21:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-11/ty-article-magazine/.premium/lihi-lapid-wife-of-ex-pm-discovers-grim-new-reality-for-israeli-authors-in-america/0000018f-fea3-d5ad-ad8f-feeb80280000</guid></item><item><title>为什么埃尔多安认为以色列想要征服土耳其</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-erdogan-thinks-israel-wants-to-conquer-turkey/00000190-02b1-d067-adb0-8eb73eb30000</link><description>最近几周，土耳其总统埃尔多安一再指责以色列密谋加沙后接管土耳其腹地，同时赞扬哈马斯是安纳托利亚的“第一道防线”。这是一种古怪的阴谋论，深深植根于埃尔多安的传记、反犹太主义和他当前的政治困境</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:32:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article-magazine/.premium/why-erdogan-thinks-israel-wants-to-conquer-turkey/00000190-02b1-d067-adb0-8eb73eb30000</guid></item><item><title>联合国安理会批准决议呼吁停火、释放人质</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-approves-resolution-calling-for-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000190-03c4-dd57-abb4-7bce65a90000</link><description>14个国家对该提案投了赞成票，俄罗斯投了弃权票 ■ 内塔尼亚胡政府公开反对该决议的框架</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 20:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/un-security-council-approves-resolution-calling-for-cease-fire-hostage-release/00000190-03c4-dd57-abb4-7bce65a90000</guid></item><item><title>真正的反对派会站出来吗：有人试图将以色列从内塔尼亚胡、无休止的战争和孤立中拯救出来吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/is-anyone-trying-to-save-israel-from-netanyahu-isolation-and-endless-war/00000190-0312-de5e-a5ff-2796ae980000</link><description>本尼·甘茨毫不奇怪地离开内塔尼亚胡政府，这不会增强反对派的力量，因为以色列几乎没有名副其实的反对派。这对于结束加沙战争和巴以冲突来说是个坏消息</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 19:27:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/is-anyone-trying-to-save-israel-from-netanyahu-isolation-and-endless-war/00000190-0312-de5e-a5ff-2796ae980000</guid></item><item><title>以色列人对欧洲“亲以色列”极右势力的崛起感到高兴</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-10/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-myopic-rejoicing-over-the-rise-of-europes-pro-israel-far-right/00000190-031d-d5ad-ad93-275d113b0000</link><description>以色列人最好听取欧洲拉比会议主席拉比·平查斯·戈尔德施密特等人物的意见，他在欧盟大选前夕写道，欧洲犹太人“没有好的选择”</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 18:21:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/haaretz-today/2024-06-10/ty-article/.highlight/israelis-myopic-rejoicing-over-the-rise-of-europes-pro-israel-far-right/00000190-031d-d5ad-ad93-275d113b0000</guid></item><item><title>以色列战争第 248 天：联合国安理会将就支持停战提案的决议进行投票</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</link><description>据报道，拜登政府正在讨论与哈马斯达成协议，以防涉及以色列的谈判失败，释放被关押在加沙的五名美国公民 ■ 美国国务卿布林肯自 10 月 7 日以来第八次访问以色列 ■ 联合国安理会将就美国决议进行投票支持拜登提出的停战提案 ■ 一架以色列无人机在黎巴嫩被击落 ■ 战争进入 248 天后，您需要了解以下内容</description><pubDate>Mon, 10 Jun 2024 17:03:49 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2024-06-10/ty-article/.premium/israel-at-war-day-248-un-security-council-to-vote-on-resolution-backing-truce-proposal/00000190-02f5-de5e-a5ff-27f793a90001</guid></item></channel></rss>